                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/134839191/">知夏Hecate</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-09-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">黑话多，难啃。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
        <p>&gt; <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1060125/comments/">更多短评 31 条</a></p>
